Spring MVC controller for requesting an access token for the prosEO ODIP API; implements the services required to provide a RESTful API according to OAuth2 "Resource Owner Password Credentials Grant" flow and "Client Credentials Grant" flow as requested in ESA's Production Interface Delivery Point (ODIP) API ICD (ESA-EOPG-EOPGC-IF-3, issue 1.5) and its associated "Technical Note for the Interface Delivery Points Access and Authentication" (issue 1.0).
